    "_scoring_notes": "Scoring Part A.If four or more marks appear in the darkly shaded boxes within Part A, then the patient has symptoms highly consistent with ADHD in adults, and further investigation is warranted.Part B.The frequency scores on Part B provide additional cues and can serve as further probes into the patient's symptoms. Pay particular attention to marks appearing in the darkly shaded boxes. No total score or diagnostic likelihood is utilized for the twelve questions."
